      <p class="section-sub">Every workflow a modern store needs — transactions, inventory, fulfillment, clienteling, and operations — in one iOS-native interface, backed by native <a href="/platform/rfid/" style="color: var(--brand-text);">RFID</a> and real-time <a href="/platform/inventory-control/" style="color: var(--brand-text);">Inventory Control</a>.</p>
